And let me say the hard part. If you keep going back to it, you don't have a porn problem. You have a worship problem. You're worshiping comfort, escape, fantasy, and the fake intimacy of a screen that asks nothing of you. Repent of the worship, not just the behavior. There's a difference, and your soul knows it.

